ygData.messageBody:
Some one axed about Phinias Autowhoziss(sp?) - the Kedge Keep bossman?
Found a screen shot for ya:

http://www.sba.uwm.edu/jgs/sylly/phinias.jpg
<http://www.sba.uwm.edu/jgs/sylly/phinias.jpg>

Enjoy,

Sylly

p.s. looking for something to solo now that Avo's are green? Try Goblin
Netmasters in Lake Rathe. Giving xp at level 43. Track them from the Flame
Tower Island. What no fishbone earring? Tsk, tsk, stock up on endure breath
potion or fishscales and beg your friendly ranger druids. Nasty casters,
shallow water swimmers. After getting run out of the water a couple times
because the pally I was helping get his quest junk could not keep up with
the fight, DUH chain & fear work good! Keep a DD spell handy too. Melee
combat is difficult in the water.
